---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";

import Nav from "../components/Nav.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout title="Simpletodo.app: Privacy">
  <Nav />
  <main>
    <section class="py-12 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-normal text-center mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>

        <p class="text-lg mb-6">
          At Simpletodo.app, your privacy is our priority. This Privacy Policy
          explains how we handle your data when you use our application and
          visit our website. We are committed to protecting your information and
          ensuring transparency about what data we collect and how it is used.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Desktop App Privacy Policy</h2>

        <h3 class="text-base font-semibold mb-2">Offline Usage</h3>
        <p class="mb-6">
          Our app is designed for offline use, meaning that none of your tasks,
          notes, or todo items are transmitted or stored on external servers.
          All data remains on your device, and we do not collect or process this
          information.
        </p>

        <h3 class="text-base font-semibold mb-2">No Tracking</h3>
        <p class="mb-6">
          We do not use any form of tracking, analytics, or advertising software
          in our app. Your activity within the app is entirely private and never
          shared with third parties.
        </p>

        <h3 class="text-base font-semibold mb-2">Changes to this Policy</h3>
        <p class="mb-6">
          We may occasionally update this Privacy Policy to reflect changes in
          our practices. If significant updates are made, we will notify you via
          the app or email. We encourage you to review this policy periodically.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Website Privacy Policy</h2>

        <h3 class="text-base font-semibold mb-2">Data Collection</h3>
        <p class="mb-6">
          When you visit our website, we may collect anonymous data to better
          understand how users interact with our site and to improve our
          services.
        </p>

        <p class="mb-6">
          Our website may contain links to external sites not operated by us.
          Please note that we have no control over the content and practices of
          these sites and cannot accept responsibility for their privacy
          policies.
        </p>

        <p class="mb-6">
          Your continued use of our website will be regarded as acceptance of
          our privacy practices. If you have any questions about how we handle
          user data, feel free to contact us.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Contact Information</h2>
        <p class="mb-6">
          If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy,
          please contact us at:
        </p>
        <p class="mb-6">
          <strong>Email</strong>: <a
            href="mailto:support@simpletodo.app"
            class="text-blue-500 hover:underline">support@simpletodo.app</a
          >
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
